00:24:03,074 --> 00:24:04,974
What the hell
you talking about a rose?

413
00:24:05,076 --> 00:24:07,510
What would you people
from southern New Jersey know?

414
00:24:07,612 --> 00:24:09,910
Oh-ho.
Beautiful woman.

415
00:24:10,015 --> 00:24:12,108
These two are exquisite. Look at them.

416
00:24:12,217 --> 00:24:14,549
<i>It's really
hard to describe oneself...</i>

417
00:24:14,653 --> 00:24:17,986
<i>because I think one lives very often
in other people's visions.</i>

418
00:24:18,089 --> 00:24:23,117
I see myself as the world's oldest living
teenager 'cause I have such a good time,

419
00:24:23,228 --> 00:24:26,823
and I try to get as much kick
out of things as possible.

420
00:24:26,932 --> 00:24:30,424
I have all my little animals, who,
by the way, are very jealous of me,

421
00:24:30,535 --> 00:24:33,527
and so I have to give them jewelry...
otherwise they bite.

